Fish don't fry
in the kitchen

00:25.887 --> 00:28.511
Beans don't burn
on the grill

00:28.649 --> 00:30.996
Took a whole lot of tryin'

00:31.134 --> 00:33.723
Just to get up that hill

00:33.861 --> 00:36.346
Now we're up
in the big leagues

00:36.484 --> 00:38.969
Gettin' our turn at bat

00:39.108 --> 00:41.420
As long as we live
it's you and me, baby

00:41.558 --> 00:43.560
